START:
PRC ENTER A NUMBER:
REA
SET N
PUS 2
SET X

LOOP:
GET N
GET X
GTH
JIZ PRIME
GET N
GET X
MOD
JIZ NOPRIME
GET X
PUS 1
ADD
SET X
JUM LOOP

PRIME:
PRC NUMBER IS A PRIME
PRC DO YOU WANNA START AGAIN? YES (1), NO (0)
REA
JIT START
STP

NOPRIME:
PRC NUMBER IS NOT A PRIME
PRC DO YOU WANNA START AGAIN? YES (1), NO (0)
REA
JIT START
STP